{"type":"message","id":"955926b7","parentId":"2cf7d151","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:55:18.093Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f4ae4f45cb0c441f8f8f09ccf3]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 底层自带多 Agent 互通、任务拆分、协同对话，不用额外装插件，只开 2 个核心参数\n\n2. 全局配置开启互通\n\n找到config.json写入：\njson\n```PLAIN_TEXT\n{\n \"multi_agent_enable\": true,\n \"agent_chat_visible\": true,\n \"share_context_pool\": true\n}\n```\n\n\n\\- multi\\_agent\\_enable：开启多智能体调度\n\n\\- agent\\_chat\\_visible：智能体互相看见对话\n\n\\- share\\_context\\_pool：共用上下文记忆\n\n这些说的对阿妈，"}],"timestamp":1778903718087}}
