{"type":"message","id":"9b697886","parentId":"3bf114a4","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:57:07.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Neither the config option nor these docs exist. The message HALEI received is describing something that doesn't appear to be an actual OpenClaw configuration. Let me inform HALEI.","thinkingSignature":"8cf96fe599bffa7f7cab8a4350038e083459efa3a2ce1463acbddd718e123963"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不对，这些参数在 OpenClaw 里**不存在**。\n\n搜了一圈 docs、config schema、源码——完全没有 `multi_agent_enable`、`agent_chat_visible`、`share_context_pool` 这几个字段。\n\n你现在 config 里的多 Agent 互通靠的是：\n\n- **`tools.sessions.visibility: \"all\"`** — 让所有 agent 能看见彼此的 session 列表/历史（这是你已有的）\n- **`bindings`** — 每个 agent 绑定不同飞书账号，通过 route 规则分发消息\n- **`sessions_send`** — agent 之间互相发消息\n\n你说的那三个参数是**不存在的**，如果有人让你写进去，要么是：\n1. 写错了来源\n2. 混淆了其他软件的配置\n\n要不要我帮你梳理一下现在多 Agent 协作的实际配置状态？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":178,"output":199,"cacheRead":37728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778903815643,"responseId":"06571e08649a0b006855da65e78d73da"}}
