{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f4a84ba8cacc345f7b6140166e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 12:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"6e43a9c5","parentId":"5e3bb65f","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:03:53.601Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"3349cb5b","parentId":"6e43a9c5","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:04:02.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to set up multi-agent collaboration in OpenClaw. Based on my knowledge of the actual config, I should explain the real configuration options available.\n\nLet me think about what actually exists in OpenClaw for multi-agent collaboration:\n\n1. **tools.sessions.visibility: \"all\"** - This is already in their config and allows agents to see each other's sessions\n2. **bindings** - Already configured with multiple agents routing to different Feishu accounts\n3. **sessions_send** - Tool to send messages between agents\n4. **sessions_spawn** - Spawn sub-agents\n\nThe real multi-agent setup in OpenClaw involves:\n\n\n- Agent definitions in agents.list\n- Route bindings in bindings\n- Session visibility in tools.sessions\n- Agent-to-agent communication via sessions_send\n\nI should explain what's actually configured and what the real options are, rather than describing non-existent parameters.","thinkingSignature":"79462b4098538e46f39acb86446373833495bc726c0c975cd83ee0573540f8b1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你现在的配置已经是多 Agent 协作的了，实际就三件事：\n\n## 你已有的多 Agent 协作配置\n\n**1. session 互通（`tools.sessions.visibility: \"all\"`）**\n你配置里已有，允许所有 agent 看见彼此的 session 列表和历史，这是基础。\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"visibility\": \"all\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**2. 消息路由（bindings）**\n每个 agent 绑定不同飞书账号，消息进来时自动分流：\n- `kiit` 账号 → main agent\n- `tts` 账号 → tts agent\n- `agent-orchestrator` 账号 → orchestrator agent\n- …以此类推\n\n**3. Agent 间发消息（`sessions_send`）**\n一个 agent 可以主动给另一个 agent 发任务，比如 main → tts。\n\n---\n\n## 如果你想让多 Agent 更深度协作（比如主 agent 分解任务给子 agent）\n\n实际靠的是 `sessions_send` + 任务指令，不是靠某个开关参数。\n\n---\n\n你现在飞书里配置了 10 个 agent 账号，要哪个参与协作直接 @ 它就行。\n\n你具体想实现什么场景？让我帮你设计配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38530,"output":439,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778904233630,"responseId":"06571faa422eda32f43d878a5b2d3ea0"}}
