{"type":"message","id":"87a80d47","parentId":"20ca8d97","timestamp":"2026-05-16T08:52:38.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the memory architecture in OpenClaw, and specifically why the TK选品大师 (tts agent) doesn't remember conversations from yesterday.\n\nLet me think about what I know about OpenClaw's memory architecture:\n\n1. **memory-core** - Built-in core memory plugin\n2. **sqlite-vec** - Built-in local vector indexing\n3. **MEMORY.md + daily.md** - Long-term file memory\n4. **.dreams/** - Vector corpus storage\n\nThe key question is: each agent has their own workspace, and the tts agent likely has its own workspace (`workspace-tts`). The memory files are per-workspace.\n\n\nSo the real problem is that memory doesn't automatically sync across workspaces—each agent maintains its own context. The user would need to either explicitly share memory files between them or establish a shared knowledge base that both can access.\n\nFor the tts agent specifically, it should have access to its own workspace memory files like `MEMORY.md` and daily notes, but these won't include what was discussed in other sessions unless there's a deliberate sharing mechanism in place.\n\nThe compaction process might be consolidating older conversation history, which could make it seem like the agent has forgotten earlier context. I should check what memory sources the tts workspace actually has access to and trace through how the conversation history gets managed.\n","thinkingSignature":"3f51fa84267cd7073c1a2cd77c5eb38e1a8550cc4251df211c8468e85159e47a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这个问题很实在，让我先查一下 tts agent 的 workspace 记忆状况。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_27nv4x6aii7t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-tts/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"---\" && cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"MEMORY.md not found\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_27nv4x6aii7t_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-tts/memory/ 2>/dev/null && cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-tts/memory/*.md 2>/dev/null | head -100 || echo \"no memory dir\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38017,"output":442,"cacheRead":1024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778921541411,"responseId":"06576345ac1388d6be9fae30abce920e"}}
