{"type":"message","id":"b60be8bc","parentId":"ea452344","timestamp":"2026-05-16T08:53:42.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the TTS workspace is at `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`, and its memory directory only has a `dreaming` subfolder. There's no MEMORY.md or daily memory files.\n\nThis is the issue - the TTS agent's workspace has no persistent memory files. It only has a `dreaming` folder (for lossless-claw vector storage presumably) but no MEMORY.md or memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md files.\n\nLet me explain the memory architecture to HALEI and specifically address why TTS doesn't remember.\n\nThe memory architecture in OpenClaw:\n1. **memory-core** plugin - handles the memory system\n2. **MEMORY.md** - long-term memory file per workspace\n\n\n3. **memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md** - daily logs\n4. **.dreams/** - vector store for semantic recall (lossless-claw)\n5. **sqlite-vec** - local vector index\n\nThe TTS workspace is missing MEMORY.md and daily log files entirely, which explains why it has no persistent memory. I need to outline what's needed to fix this.","thinkingSignature":"6f09b85e31091d9004e203a18704728c7e33ec2bf2607a78d6f4ab006ab1a5b4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到问题了。TTS 的 workspace 里**没有记忆文件**。\n\n## OpenClaw 记忆架构\n\n每个 Agent 的记忆由这几层构成：\n\n| 层级 | 作用 | 位置 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **MEMORY.md** | 长期记忆，精选重要信息 | `{workspace}/MEMORY.md` |\n| **memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md** | 每日日志，记录当天发生的事 | `{workspace}/memory/` |\n| **.dreams/** | 向量语义记忆，支撑语义检索 | `{workspace}/.dreams/` |\n| **lossless-claw** | 对话历史压缩/召回 | 自动 |\n\n---\n\n## 为什么 TTS 不记得\n\n你的 TTS workspace 在 `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`，现状：\n\n```\nworkspace-tts/\n├── memory/dreaming/   ← 只有这个，向量存储\n├── AGENTS.md\n├── SOUL.md\n├── USER.md\n└── …（没有 MEMORY.md，没有 memory/*.md）\n```\n\n**它没有写 MEMORY.md 和每日日志，所以每次醒来就是空的。**\n\n---\n\n## 怎么解决\n\nTTS 的 workspace 目录里需要加上：\n1. `MEMORY.md` — 长期记忆文件\n2. `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — 每日日志（比如 `memory/2025-05-15.md`）\n\n要我帮 TTS 初始化记忆文件结构吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":153,"output":522,"cacheRead":42336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43011,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778921599932,"responseId":"0657638009b146bece620282b99d555b"}}
