{"type":"message","id":"d0d63d70","parentId":"0305849e","timestamp":"2026-05-16T08:55:46.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create the MEMORY.md and memory/2026-05-16.md files for the TTS workspace.\n","thinkingSignature":"78b044dcdbd367b223c1071dec8a331990525f461cb1651ca6af46128c7302c9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3fbsbxwujqp0_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n每次醒来都会读这个文件。惜字如金，只留真正重要的。\n\n## 用户信息\n- 用户通过飞书与 TK 选品大师对话\n- 代号：TK 选品大师（TTS Agent）\n- 专注：TikTok 选品相关的分析和建议\n\n## 索引\n\n> `memory/` 下的文件索引。新建文件时在此添加条目。\n\n- YYYY-MM-DD.md: 每日日志\n\n## 已知偏好\n\n（随对话补充）\n\n## 待记\n\n（待补充）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3fbsbxwujqp0_2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-05-16\n\n## 今天做了什么\n\n- 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志\n- 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`\n- 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n\n## 待记\n\n- 用户的选品偏好（待补充）\n- 重要选品决策（待补充）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-05-16.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56,"output":329,"cacheRead":44192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778921740850,"responseId":"0657640d93ea70032bfe1d04a8dcb75c"}}
